videos.description: Charles Matthews draws a foul after a perfect cut to the basket for an easy bucket for Michigan.
videos.headline: Michigan runs perfect play for Matthews score

videos.description: Moritz Wagner gets an easy dunk after Zavier Simpson throws a beautiful one-handed pass.
videos.headline: Michigan's Simpson throws a dime to Wagner

videos.description: Charles Matthews tallies 15 points and 7 rebounds at the half for Michigan against Chaminade.
videos.headline: Michigan's Matthews knocks down a 3 just before halftime

videos.description: Duncan Robinson knocks down an open three-pointer in transition after a Charles Matthews block.
videos.headline: Michigan turns a block into a 3 in transition

videos.description: Michigan's Moritz Wagner finishes in transition with a dunk after a great pass from Muhammad Abdur-Rahkman.
videos.headline: Wagner finishes alley-oop on the break
